==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Dell
<hw>Dell</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[AS. <ets>del</ets>, akin
to E. <ets>dale</ets>; cf. D. <ets>delle</ets>, <ets>del</ets>, low
ground. See <er>Dale</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A small, retired
valley; a ravine.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>In <qex>dells</qex> and dales, concealed from human sight.</q>
<rj><qau>Tickell.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A young woman; a wench.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Sweet doxies and <qex>dells</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>B.
Jonson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Della Crusca</ent>⟦br⟧
\'d8
